This is a great scope that mag that is crystal clear and great eye relief.  Practically brand new set up on 7X Magnifier and BURRIS AR PIVOT RING. It's just to long range for me the, the AR PIVOT MOUNT has a quick attach/detach and a push button that flips the mount clear to side of primary scope.  The Quick attach BURRIS AR PIVOT RING  works wonders folds out of the way when you don't need it and folds back to the scope when you need the extra magnification with a push of a button. Or you can just detach in a second or reattach it in a second.  The mount alone sells for over $100,  the 7x glass on the magnification makes an excellent auxiliary scope.  And is very clear with great adjustable eye relief. Works great
